top_visible_issues: No website found — the business has no online presence
No Google Business listing identified — the business is not discoverable through local search
No review or trust data available — the business cannot be evaluated or found by potential customers searching online
outreach_hook: Example Cafe is an active local business in Westport with no website or Google Business listing currently identified. For a hospitality business, establishing both would create a clear online foundation and ensure the cafe appears when people search for cafes in the area.
